   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-f" mid="189" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="162"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>On the day of the Dragon Raid….<BR>While we were climbing the Black Mountain, an army of red monsters showed up on the other side of the mountain.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-g" mid="191" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="190"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>The red army… it must be Elena.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-g" image="QM_Ellena.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-h" mid="192" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>Yes, <FONT color=#a82424>Dark Elf Elena</FONT> came with the Red Army. At that time we thought Red Army was the supporter of Black Dragon.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-h" image="QN_Npc_Argenta.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-i" mid="193" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>On our side <FONT color=#a82424>Argenta</FONT> stayed behind to take care of the Red Army and the rest continued to Foothills of Black Mountain, where Black Dragon was.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-i" image="QM_black_Dragon.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-j" mid="194" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>However, the Black Dragon was much stronger than we expected.... It took the Black Dragon less than one hour to wipe out our entire army.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-j" image="QN_Npc_Geraint.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-k" mid="195" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>When everyone else was in despair, Geraint stepped forward.<BR>He said <FONT color=#a82424>"Humans, I'm sorry,"</FONT> and turned into the Gold Dragon to fight the Black Dragon.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-k" image="QN_knight_velskud.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-l" mid="196" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>It did not take long for us to be overcome with a sense of betrayal.<BR>Barnac and Nerwin who trusted Geraint with everything were deeply shocked.<BR>So was <FONT color=#a82424>Velskud</FONT>...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-l" image="QN_knight_velskud.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-m" mid="197" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>He was the most shocked among us. Barnac and Terramai had to take care of him. Velskud didn't move a step and stared at Geraint throughout the whole fight.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-m" image="QN_knight_velskud.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-n" mid="198" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>It was when Geraint became human again after the fight. He was holding the Black Dragon treasure, suddenly Velskud rushed at him, slashed his eye and took the treasure of Black Dragon.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-n" image="QN_knight_velskud.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-o" mid="200" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="199"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Geraint's eye…?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-o" image="QN_Npc_Velskud.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-p" mid="201" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>Yes, Velskud took it.<BR>Anyway, Velskud had the Black Dragon's jewel in his hand.<BR>
Then the jewel was absorbed into Velskud.<BR>
Everything happened in a split second....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-p" image="QM_Ellena.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-q" mid="202" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$CKaracule Fairystar$<BR>I'm sure he didn't expect that either. Velskud was writhing in severe pain after absorbing the jewel.<BR>
Then, Dark Elf Elena came and took Velskud away.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-q" image="QN_Npc_Argenta.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-r" mid="203" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="169"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>When Argenta came back, she too disappeared with Geraint.<BR>Without any explanation, without saying goodbye to us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-s" mid="204" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>That was it.<BR>Everything was in a mess and all we had left was chaos and wounds.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n701_oldkarakule-1-s" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_OldKarakule.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n701_oldkarakule-1-t" mid="205" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="172"><![CDATA[<html>$Karacule Fairystar$<BR>Barnac, Nerwin and I who were tainted with the blood of Black Dragon returned to our hometowns.<BR>With the useless title of '<FONT color=#a94407>heroes</FONT>'.</html>]]></talk_question>
